<i>but these appear to be isolated cases.</i>

01:21:08.840 --> 01:21:09.841
<i>Uh...</i>

01:21:09.920 --> 01:21:11.843
<i>Just to rehash,</i>

01:21:11.920 --> 01:21:15.447
<i>things appear to be back to normal
after what is certainly</i>

01:21:15.520 --> 01:21:19.081
<i>the most curious series of events
to befall this community since the...</i>

